      "content": "hey, so i got prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm. i've been taking them for 3 days now and the redness and swelling are basically gone. i feel totally fine. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to",
