      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor didn't even mention anything about resistance, he just said take them until they're gone. plus, if the infection is already gone, isn't it just extra unnecessary stress on my liver and kidneys to keep taking them for another week? it seems like more harm than good if the problem is already solved.",
